{"ECARDINES":[{"def":"An order of Brachiopoda; the Lyopomata.","pos":""}],"ECARTE":[{"def":"A game at cards, played usually by two persons, in which the players may discard any or all of the cards dealt and receive others from the pack.","pos":""}],"ECAUDATE":[{"def":"Without a tail or spur.","pos":""}]}